{
  "stem": "7600.4",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the mist turned into rain, and we just stood there all day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't go out to eat anywhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I couldn't call my mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't have a phone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We just stood there all day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was raining, and we all got soaking wet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And yet, we didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] they wouldn't let us in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was no place to call.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's not like here where there are phones everywhere.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And you will have to go someplace and know who to call, where to call him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It came to be 5:00, and we were just discussing how long we should still stand there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The door opened and he came out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he stood there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I'll never forget.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He was a nice, young man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He stood out there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Oh, he wasn't that young.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Anyway.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he apologized.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, you know, something awful happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And therefore, it was-- what happened?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It seems that in France, in Paris, a-- a Polish Jew got into the German Embassy and tried to shoot the ambassador.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know whether you know that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all he got was a secretary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He shot somebody.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they had no-- they didn't-- they hadn't taken over France yet, so they had nothing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They couldn't do anything in France.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So, but they were-- could do everything in all the other countries that they still-- they had, which was Austria and Germany and [INAUDIBLE] and all the places that they-- so they were really nasty to all the Jews.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they weren't going to let anybody out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were going to do anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he came out and he explained this horrible thing happened and he was-- they stopped him from doing most everything.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
